            <title><![CDATA[[疑问]#指甲长白点是缺钙吗#？指甲上长白点有两种情况。白甲症✅ 指甲上白点、白线是白甲症，常发生于甲半月部，随着指甲生长移至甲缘，多为原发性。不需要治疗...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%8C%87%E7%94%B2%E9%95%BF%E7%99%BD%E7%82%B9%E6%98%AF%E7%BC%BA%E9%92%99%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%8C%87%E7%94%B2%E9%95%BF%E7%99%BD%E7%82%B9%E6%98%AF%E7%BC%BA%E9%92%99%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#指甲长白点是缺钙吗#</span></a>？<br><br>指甲上长白点有两种情况。<br><br>白甲症✅ 指甲上白点、白线是白甲症，常发生于甲半月部，随着指甲生长移至甲缘，多为原发性。不需要治疗，除了影响美观之外并无大碍。<br><br>外伤导致✅ 指甲不小心受伤，被局部磨损，出现白色斑点。由于指甲生长速度较慢，可能你会在几周后才看到。<br><br>但无论是哪一种情况，都和缺钙没关系。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（科普中国）<img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hljusad4o9g20es0boquh.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
